title: Aunt Kitty's Foods Inc. Recalls Canned Chicken Products Due to Possible Processing Deviation
summary: WASHINGTON, June 26, 2018 Aunt Kittys Foods, Inc., a Vineland, N.J. establishment, is recalling approximately 10,805 pounds of canned chicken gravy products due to a possible processing deviation that may have led to underprocessing of products, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection...
